    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a" id="ref1">
      <head>Scope and Content</head>
      <p>The collection consists of Roanoke Hospital Association administrative records. Records
        include By-Laws for Roanoke Hospital Association, 1931; Report of the Secretary and
        Treasurer, 1939; hospital development materials; and pamphlets about the fund campaign for
        the Roanoke Hospital, c.1950.</p>
    </scopecontent>
